Small sections of lake bottom in shallows coming up- every year- same problem.  Very stinky.

Snails all over- small pike - no good.  No floating bogs.
Lots of rain- fewer floating bogs.  Lots of snails all over everything.  Have to get the northern out- ruining our lake.

Very nice.  Snails all over everything.  Many small northern.

great weather.  4 geese.  Two years ago there were probably 44 geese on the lake regularly.  Very happy to see so few.
